title: Brooklyn Musicians Produce Remix on Lenovo Yoga
description: Brooklyn-based musicians Spirit Guide and COSYCOS took Lenovo's IdeaPad Yoga for a test drive, working collaboratively to remix a COSYCOS track on the Yoga PC. Follow the link to download the remix from SoundCloud http://lnv.gy/T8FSo9
